title: Late One Night (Christian Movie)
description:
Late One Night (Christian Movie)

One of Rich Christiano best films. A very evangelistic film. Excellent Movie.

Three factory workers make their routine stop at a diner late one night. Just before closing, a man comes in and takes a seat at the counter. One of the workers, an antogonist named Larry, tries to strike up a conversation with a man but he does not respond,. What follows is an intense drama about the most important issue in life. 

This film gives a powerful presentation of the gospel and is very evangelistic! 
Highly recommended for teen to adult audiences. If financially possible, please buy the DVD to keep Christian films running ......

Language: English
Subtitles: None
Running Time: 33 min
My Rating: 10/10

Please seed for as long as possible. Let others also come to know that there is Salvation only in the name of Jesus Christ.

Uploaded by Indian Christian
